‚ö° NEXT: THE FIVE MANIFESTATION TYPES
This is HOW Resolve Energy actually manifests as powers.

You mentioned "five types" in your documents. Let's build them properly.

üî• THE FIVE MANIFESTATION TYPES
These are the CATEGORIES of how Resolve Energy expresses itself through a person's Core and Conviction.

Think of it like:

Resolve Energy = electricity
The Five Types = how that electricity gets used (motor, light, heat, etc.)
WHAT WE NEED TO DEFINE:
I'll give you OPTIONS for each of the five categories, and you pick what fits your vision.

Then we'll define:

Strengths/weaknesses
How they interact
Rarity
Examples from your cast
üéØ THE FIVE TYPES - OPTIONS
OPTION SET A: Classical Elements + Abstract
ENFORCEMENT (Physical enhancement, raw power)
PROJECTION (Ranged attacks, constructs)
MANIPULATION (Control of external forces)
TRANSMUTATION (Transformation, adaptation)
DENIAL (Defense, negation, barriers)
Pros: Clear, balanced, easy to understand Cons: Somewhat generic

OPTION SET B: Action-Based
STRIKE (Offense, destruction, overwhelming force)
SHIELD (Defense, protection, endurance)
FLOW (Speed, mobility, momentum)
BIND (Control, restriction, manipulation)
SHIFT (Transformation, adaptation, change)
Pros: Intuitive, combat-focused Cons: Less mystical

OPTION SET C: Philosophical (My Recommendation)
ASSERTION (Imposing your will - offense, overwhelming)
NEGATION (Denying external forces - defense, barriers)
REDIRECTION (Changing flow - momentum, control)
MANIFESTATION (Creating from nothing - constructs, projection)
TRANSMUTATION (Becoming something else - adaptation, transformation)
Pros: Thematic, deep, fits your Conviction system perfectly Cons: Requires explanation

OPTION SET D: Hybrid Approach
KINETIC (Movement, force, momentum - Aka, Sara)
VITAL (Life, healing, enhancement - Daichi)
SPATIAL (Distance, barriers, zones - Captain Kurosawa)
MATERIAL (Creating/changing matter - constructs, weapons)
SENSORY (Perception, illusion, detection - Mitsuki)
Pros: Unique, fits your characters perfectly Cons: Not perfectly balanced for combat

OPTION SET E: Your Own Names
Tell me the vibe you want and I'll build custom categories.

üéØ BASED ON YOUR CHARACTERS, HERE'S WHAT I SEE:
From your cast:

Tetsu = Foresight (sensory/prediction)
Aka = Momentum (kinetic/force)
Kaito = Fire (elemental/energy)
Sara = Lightning (elemental/energy)
Daichi = Healing (vital/restoration)
Mitsuki = Stealth (spatial/sensory)
Captain = Zone control (spatial/defensive)
Ren = Dulling field (negation/control)
They don't fit cleanly into traditional categories.

