Use OPTION C (Philosophical) with adjustments:

THE FIVE TYPES:
ENFORCEMENT (Imposing force)
Direct power, overwhelming attacks, physical enhancement
Examples: Aka (momentum), Jiro (blade strikes)
PROJECTION (External manifestation)
Creating constructs, ranged attacks, elemental expression
Examples: Kaito (fire), Sara (lightning)
DENIAL (Negation/Defense)
Barriers, nullification, zone control, suppression
Examples: Captain (Unyielding Zone), Ren (Dulling Field)
