Changing self or matter, adaptation, healing
Examples: Daichi (healing flames), potential future characters
PERCEPTION (Sensory/Mental)
Enhanced senses, prediction, illusions, stealth
Examples: Tetsu (Foresight), Mitsuki (stealth/charms)
