‚úÖ One Primary Classification per person (determined by their Conviction's nature)

‚úÖ Ability Types are unique to each person (two Manifestation users can have completely different powers)

‚úÖ Techniques are personal (how YOU use your specific ability)

‚úÖ Advanced users can develop hybrid applications (using principles from other classifications)

‚úÖ The Lost have no classification (chaotic, random Resolve expression)

