Staking EVERYTHING on one moment
Channeling all remaining Resolve into a single attack/defense
"All or nothing"
Mechanics:

Commit 100% of your Resolve + your Conviction itself
If successful: overwhelming power, guaranteed impact
If failed: Core shatters permanently ‚Üí become Hollow
When it's used:

Absolute desperation
Protecting something more important than your life
Final stand
Visual:

Aura blazes white-hot
Core glows visibly through skin
Body trembles under the strain
Everything or nothing
Consequences:

Success: Survive but completely drained (days to recover)
Failure: Core Death (Hollow)
Extremely rare. Most people die before considering it.

