What this accomplishes: ‚úÖ Immediate mystery ‚úÖ Shows consequences first ‚úÖ "What happened?" hook ‚úÖ Dual personality revealed dramatically ‚úÖ Unique structure

Risks: ‚ùå Can feel gimmicky ‚ùå Flashback structure can confuse ‚ùå Requires precise execution

Best for: Mystery-thriller tone, psychological focus

