What this accomplishes: ‚úÖ Introduces R7 squad cleanly ‚úÖ Establishes hierarchy ‚úÖ Shows procedure/world structure ‚úÖ Multiple characters at once

Risks: ‚ùå Can feel procedural/dry ‚ùå Delayed action ‚ùå Requires balancing multiple characters early

Best for: Ensemble cast focus, military-style stories

üî• MY RECOMMENDATION (for YOUR story specifically):
HYBRID: OPTION 1 + OPTION 2
Open with MICRO character moment (15 seconds), THEN immediate action.

Structure:

1. Tetsu doing something small/relatable (3-4 lines)
2. Aka makes a comment
3. Alarm/mission call interrupts
4. IMMEDIATE action scene
5. Cold open mid-fight
Example:

