"You're going to die today."

"Good morning to you too," Tetsu muttered.

The alarm screamed before Aka could respond.

---

The Lost's claws were inches from his throat when Tetsu realized Aka might've been right.
Why this works: ‚úÖ 10-second character hook (relatability) ‚úÖ Shows dual personality immediately (tone) ‚úÖ Then INSTANT high-octane action (adrenaline) ‚úÖ Best of both worlds ‚úÖ Sets up their banter dynamic ‚úÖ No slow build, but not context-free chaos

