Pure malice
Destructive nihilism
"If I suffer, everyone suffers"
Morally:

Irredeemable (by choice)
Must be stopped
TYPE 2: THE PHILOSOPHICAL (Rare - 20%)
Nature:

Conscious, intelligent
See themselves as enlightened
Reject society's values
"I awakened to the truth of existence"
