Tetsu: [no easy answer]

Aka: "Just kill him already."

Lost: "See? Even your other half knows. There's no 
      morality here. Only power and who wields it."
They're cold because:

Their Conviction froze their compassion
Rejected emotional connection
"Heat" = life, connection, humanity
They chose cold clarity over warm delusion
Visual:

Breath visible
Air shimmers with cold
Plants frost near them
