He's just too scared to admit it.

THE SPLIT: Tetsu's Conviction fractures:

"I want to matter." (True)
"But I'm terrified of trying." (Also true)

Two equal truths. Two opposing forces.

His Anima awakens‚Äî And immediately splits.

Two Cores form in his chest:

Left: Pale blue (caution, defense, fear)
Right: Black-red (ambition, aggression, certainty)
The pain is indescribable.

Tetsu screams.

